    <url>/2024/10/28/Linux%20%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Linux-基本操作"><a href="#Linux-基本操作" class="headerlink" title="Linux 基本操作"></a>Linux 基本操作</h2><h3 id="1-centos-换源为阿里云"><a href="#1-centos-换源为阿里云" class="headerlink" title="1.centos 换源为阿里云"></a>1.centos 换源为阿里云</h3><p>在 CentOS 7 上使用阿里云的源进行软件下载，可以按照以下步骤操作：</p><p>备份原有的 repo 文件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">mv</span> /etc/yum.repos.d /etc/yum.repos.d.bak<br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> /etc/yum.repos.d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建新的 repo 文件： 创建一个新的 repo 文件，例如 CentOS-Base.repo：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> vi /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加阿里云的源配置： 将以下内容粘贴到文件中：</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-section">[base]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=CentOS-<span class="hljs-variable">$releasever</span> - Base<br><span class="hljs-attr">baseurl</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/<span class="hljs-number">7</span>/os/<span class="hljs-variable">$basearch</span>/<br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgcheck</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgkey</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/RPM-GPG-KEY-archive<br><span class="hljs-attr">enabled</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><br><span class="hljs-section">[updates]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=CentOS-<span class="hljs-variable">$releasever</span> - Updates<br><span class="hljs-attr">baseurl</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/<span class="hljs-number">7</span>/updates/<span class="hljs-variable">$basearch</span>/<br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgcheck</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgkey</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/RPM-GPG-KEY-archive<br><span class="hljs-attr">enabled</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><br><span class="hljs-section">[extras]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=CentOS-<span class="hljs-variable">$releasever</span> - Extras<br><span class="hljs-attr">baseurl</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/<span class="hljs-number">7</span>/extras/<span class="hljs-variable">$basearch</span>/<br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgcheck</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgkey</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/RPM-GPG-KEY-archive<br><span class="hljs-attr">enabled</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><br><span class="hljs-section">[centosplus]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=CentOS-<span class="hljs-variable">$releasever</span> - Plus<br><span class="hljs-attr">baseurl</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/<span class="hljs-number">7</span>/centosplus/<span class="hljs-variable">$basearch</span>/<br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgcheck</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">gpgkey</span>=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/RPM-GPG-KEY-archive<br><span class="hljs-attr">enabled</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>清除缓存并更新： 清除 yum 缓存并更新：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> yum clean all<br><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> yum makecache<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装软件： 现在你可以使用 yum 安装软件了：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> yum install package_name<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样就可以使用阿里云的源来下载和安装软件了。</p><h3 id="2-修改固定ip"><a href="#2-修改固定ip" class="headerlink" title="2.修改固定ip"></a>2.修改固定ip</h3><p>要在 CentOS 7 上设置固定 IP 地址，可以按照以下步骤操作：</p><ol><li><p><strong>编辑网络配置文件</strong>：<br>打开对应网络接口的配置文件，通常在 <code>/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/</code> 目录下。假设你的网络接口是 <code>eth0</code>，则命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>修改或添加以下内容</strong>：<br>确保文件中包含以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-attr">TYPE</span>=Ethernet<br><span class="hljs-attr">BOOTPROTO</span>=none<br><span class="hljs-attr">NAME</span>=eth0<br><span class="hljs-attr">DEVICE</span>=eth0<br><span class="hljs-attr">ONBOOT</span>=<span class="hljs-literal">yes</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">IPADDR</span>=<span class="hljs-number">192.168</span>.<span class="hljs-number">1.100</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 替换为你的固定IP</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">NETMASK</span>=<span class="hljs-number">255.255</span>.<span class="hljs-number">255.0</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 替换为你的子网掩码</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">GATEWAY</span>=<span class="hljs-number">192.168</span>.<span class="hljs-number">1.1</span>   <span class="hljs-comment"># 替换为你的网关</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">DNS1</span>=<span class="hljs-number">8.8</span>.<span class="hljs-number">8.8</span>          <span class="hljs-comment"># 替换为你的DNS</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="3-挂起进程"><a href="#3-挂起进程" class="headerlink" title="3.挂起进程"></a>3.挂起进程</h3><p>在 Linux 系统中，可以使用 <code>kill</code> 命令结合信号来挂起某个进程。要挂起某个 PID，可以发送 <code>SIGSTOP</code> 信号：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">kill</span> -SIGSTOP &lt;PID&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>替换 <code>&lt;PID&gt;</code> 为你要挂起的进程的实际进程 ID。要恢复进程，可以发送 <code>SIGCONT</code> 信号：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">kill</span> -SIGCONT &lt;PID&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-Btrfs-文件系统"><a href="#4-Btrfs-文件系统" class="headerlink" title="4.Btrfs 文件系统"></a>4.<strong>Btrfs</strong> 文件系统</h3><p><strong>Btrfs</strong> 是一种先进的文件系统，支持快照、子卷和多挂载等特性。它通过将数据和元数据分开存储，提高了性能和可靠性。以下是一些主要功能和使用方法：</p><p><strong>主要特性</strong></p><ol><li><strong>快照</strong>：可以在任意时刻创建文件系统的只读快照，方便备份和恢复。</li><li><strong>子卷</strong>：可以创建多个子卷，每个子卷都像独立的文件系统，支持不同的挂载选项。</li><li><strong>多挂载</strong>：同一子卷可以在不同的挂载点同时挂载，允许灵活的数据共享。</li><li><strong>在线压缩</strong>：支持在数据写入时进行压缩，以节省存储空间。</li></ol><p><strong>挂载 Btrfs</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>格式化</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">mkfs.btrfs /dev/sdX<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>替换 <code>/dev/sdX</code> 为你的设备。</p></li><li><p><strong>挂载</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">mount -t btrfs /dev/sdX /mnt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>创建子卷</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">btrfs subvolume create /mnt/my_subvolume<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>挂载子卷</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">mount -o subvol=my_subvolume /dev/sdX /mnt/my_mount_point<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>使用快照</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">btrfs subvolume snapshot /mnt/my_subvolume /mnt/my_snapshot<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p><strong>多挂载</strong></p><p>要多次挂载同一个子卷，可以使用 <code>mount</code> 命令多次指定不同的挂载点。例如：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">mount -o subvol=my_subvolume /dev/sdX /mnt/point1<br>mount -o subvol=my_subvolume /dev/sdX /mnt/point2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样，可以在 <code>/mnt/point1</code> 和 <code>/mnt/point2</code> 访问同一个子卷的内容。</p><p>5. </p>]]></content>
    
    
    
